        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uC791\uC740 \uC124\uC6D0\uC758 \uD130\uC8FC, \uB098\uD0C0\uB098\uB2E4!",
